sum by(service) (
  irate(tcp_info_bytes_sent{site=~"$site", service=~"$service"}[$resolution])
  or
  irate(s3nd_s3_tcp_info_bytes_sent_total{site=~"$site", service=~"$service"}[$resolution])
) * 8
